    "poemName": "The Tale of Major Korean",
    "poemAuthor": "Bushi",
    "poemContent": {
        "type": "fragment",
        "styles": [],
        "children": [
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "I once knew a man, a sellsword , traveller, wanderer,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "His name was Major Korean, and now is recounted his tale of woe;"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " It was summer of 1923, or whenever it was auf der große streets,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " I recognised a shadow, that lurked in the corner,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " Stacks of money, all but useless"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " But the person I saw, said his name was,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " A \"Major Korean\"."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "I heard nothing more, until the second great war;"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "A rogue soldier, not a nazi in the war,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Travelled to a land unknown, fought to save many lives"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Grasped only a sword, an iron carved sword,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Stained with valour, heart of woe."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "The warrior who fought for no country, only to save the others"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Named Major \"Korean\""
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Then I saw, at the door of the gates by the court,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Tried for crimes, against the law, sat Major Korean,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Crimes that were not crimes, such as speaking against a dictatorship."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "One of the few people I knew, was Major Korean, who was an"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Anti-racist."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " But where is he now, what land does he lie,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " A slayer, what became of the man, known as"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " Major Korean?"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "This fellow, who was not even Korean, went under that alibi,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "For what, to protect which truths? Hide a life of honour?"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "That person who defeated die Leute, tried end racism,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "His fate unknown, Major Korean, the Anti-Racist."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "T'was a dark day, when I realised, he had vanished,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Off the face of the Earth."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Die Geselschaft, a great enemy, back-stabbed that warrior"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "What cave, creek or crevice did he hide, branded as a"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Threat to society?"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " I grasped a sword and trained, under the waterfall in the"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " Dead of the night, stealing my heart to be full of resolve,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " To act out justice, restore that myth's honour."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " The Mythical Major Korean."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "In those old days, when Stresemann reigned,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "How we'd all think,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "I have Weimar, my republic,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "How I'd want the Kaiser to be King!"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "But now, it seems, we were wrong..."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "The old days, age of slayers are now far gone."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Hoonter, Reece, Noct, Major Korean, Speedwagon, Zekiahepic, Barir"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Those times, am besten Zeit"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Die Zukunft war nicht zu toll..."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "But the tale does not end, no- not the take of Major Korean,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Borne in 1066, borne of blood, brother in battle to the slayers,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "The un-racist könig."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "War is coming,a great plight, so, he took up th' mantle"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "One last time."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "A final clash of steel, iron against iron,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Last march of the catgirl slayers, before stepping into new dawn..."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Major Korean fought valiantly, but comrade after comrade fell,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Bloodshed blood lets more mo'r blood"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "And the ground bleeds red,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "It was then when he said, as the dawn of the next day set;"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Tears in his eyes, tired, could not fight anymore,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "I am sorry, Bushi, Noct, Martin Ligations, Swexys, Gundalf,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Barir, Zekiahepic, Speedwagon, Samurai of the Spear, Dark Juice,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Juloo, Delta. Solaire, Solar System Man, Reece and all fellow"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Other Slayer;"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " In order, to defeat this foe, and restore this honour..."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " I must become racism..."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " It must be done, thank you everyone..."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " This truly was an adventure, wasn't it?"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Then with one final attack, a desperate last resort, a desperate last stand."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Major Korean unleashed his last attack, his final strike..."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "All the enemies were slain, at the cost of Major Korean's sacrifice,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "With a final smile, he faded away, finally at peace, at his end."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": " This was the tale of Major Korean."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 3
            }
        ]
    },
    "pageStyle": "poem-centre-wide",
    "pageBackground": ""
}